---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Contact ARM Management | International Business Advisory"
  description="Start with a confidential conversation. Every ARM engagement begins with a direct conversation with a senior advisor who will assess your situation honestly."
>
<main>

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero__bg" style="background-image:url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497366216548-37526070297c?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop')"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="page-hero__content container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Contact</span>
      <h1>Start With a Confidential<br>Conversation.</h1>
      <p>Every ARM engagement begins the same way: a direct conversation with a senior advisor who will assess your situation honestly and tell you exactly what is achievable.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cream">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="contact-grid reveal">
        <div class="contact-card">
          <span class="eyebrow">Email</span>
          <h3>Write to Us</h3>
          <p>For detailed enquiries or where you prefer to communicate in writing. A senior advisor responds within one business day.</p>
          <a href="mailto:info@arm-management.com" class="btn-navy">info@arm-management.com</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <span class="eyebrow">Schedule</span>
          <h3>Book a Consultation</h3>
          <p>Select a time that works for you. A senior ARM advisor will join the call prepared to discuss your specific situation.</p>
          <a href="mailto:info@arm-management.com?subject=Consultation Request" class="btn-navy">Request a Time →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-card">
          <span class="eyebrow">Confidentiality</span>
          <h3>Complete Discretion</h3>
          <p>ARM Management treats all enquiries with complete confidentiality. Your information is not shared with any third party. All engagements are governed by formal service agreements.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--warm" style="border-top:1px solid #E2DDD6">
    <div class="container--narrow">
      <h2 class="reveal">Send Us a Message</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule reveal"></div>
      <p class="reveal" style="color:#6B7280;margin-bottom:40px">Complete the form below and a senior ARM advisor will respond within one business day.</p>

      <form class="contact-form reveal" name="contact" method="POST" netlify netlify-honeypot="bot-field" action="/thank-you">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact">
        <p style="display:none"><input name="bot-field"></p>

        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label" for="name">Full Name *</label>
            <input class="form-input" type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Your full name">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label" for="email">Email Address *</label>
            <input class="form-input" type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your@email.com">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-row">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label" for="company">Company / Organisation</label>
            <input class="form-input" type="text" id="company" name="company" placeholder="Your company name">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label class="form-label" for="country">Country of Residence</label>
            <input class="form-input" type="text" id="country" name="country" placeholder="e.g. United Arab Emirates">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label" for="service">Service Area</label>
          <select class="form-select" id="service" name="service">
            <option value="">Select a service area</option>
            <option>Transaction Advisory</option>
            <option>Company Formation</option>
            <option>Accounting &amp; Tax</option>
            <option>Payroll &amp; HR Advisory</option>
            <option>Global Mobility &amp; Residency</option>
            <option>Crypto &amp; Web3</option>
            <option>Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label" for="message">Brief Description *</label>
          <textarea class="form-textarea" id="message" name="message" required placeholder="Please briefly describe your situation and what you need assistance with..."></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label class="form-label" for="source">How did you hear about ARM Management?</label>
          <select class="form-select" id="source" name="source">
            <option value="">Please select</option>
            <option>Google Search</option>
            <option>Referral</option>
            <option>LinkedIn</option>
            <option>Event / Conference</option>
            <option>Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary" style="border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:12px">Submit Enquiry →</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
</Base>
